{"tid":1684153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普sir：「下場唔能踢了，比牙仙奴踢！」","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T00:47:22.000Z","uid":73381,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"44893cf90a0b3032396448928c2962c58ed0ebe8","tid":1684153,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:09:31.000Z","msg":"【高普要求賽會安排合適賽期】<br />\n<br />\n在雙方不設防的對決中，利物浦以非常驚險的形勢下晉級。不過看來高普意不在聯賽盃，甚至在失去第三球時苦笑起來。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦在聯賽盃八強有可能面對曼城、曼聯、李斯特城等對手，而八強的賽程將會安排在十二月月中，正是出戰世冠盃的前夕。高普在賽後表示：「若賽會不能安排合適的賽期，我意思不是指聖誕節的凌晨三時，那麼我們放棄作賽。若果球隊不能消化整個賽程時，你必須要多加考慮，我認為這是公平的，我們不能成為問題的受害人。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們今晚踢了一場希望勝出的比賽，結果完成任務。若然賽會未能為我們排得合適賽期，我們實在無法出戰下一圈賽事，或許讓阿仙奴頂上吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://metro.co.uk/2019/10/30/jurgen-klopp-threatens-pull-liverpool-carabao-cup-arsenal-win-11015259/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2019%2F10%2F30%2Fjurgen-klopp-threatens-pull-liverpool-carabao-cup-arsenal-win-11015259%2F&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=4b56693b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://metro.co.uk/2019/10/30/jurgen-klopp-threatens-pull-liverpool-carabao-cup-arsenal-win-11015259/</a>"},{"pid":"27d71d7920de6ed3ad64de2aae5aa2f1422d1a00","tid":1684153,"uid":21842,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛 咁能串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d87933fd98b6aec6d1b6d3333addb0120cd989","tid":1684153,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a8dcd65f7f0c38c2b37f0f344c50fd9c604417","tid":1684153,"uid":38934,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:12:56.000Z","msg":"預備組踢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e57e5e089eb48